\begin{align}(\overline{P\cdot Q} + R)\cdot (\overline Q + P\cdot \overline R) &= (\overline P + \overline Q + R)\cdot(\overline Q + P\cdot \overline R) \tag{DeMorgan's} \\ \\ & =  \overline Q + (\overline P + R)(P\cdot \overline R) \tag{D.L.} \\ \\ & = \overline Q + (\color{blue}{\overline P\cdot P}\cdot \overline R) + (\color{red}{R}\cdot P\cdot \color{red}{ \overline R}) \tag{D.L.}\\ \\ & = \overline Q + \color{blue}{ 0} + \color{red}{\bf 0} \tag{
}\\ \\ &= Q'\end{align}
((PQ)' + R)(Q' + PR') = (P' + Q' + R)(Q' + PR') = Q' + (P' + R)(PR') = Q' + P'PR' + RPR' = Q' + 0 + 0 = Q'
